[DOMAIN]
(define (domain blocksworld-4ops)
  (:requirements :strips)
(:predicates (clear ?x)
             (ontable ?x)
             (handempty)
             (holding ?x)
             (on ?x ?y))

(:action pick-up

  :effect (and (handempty) (clear ?ob) (on ?ob ?underob)
               (not (clear ?underob)) (not (holding ?ob))))

(:action unstack
  :parameters  (?ob ?underob)
  :precondition (and (on ?ob ?underob) (clear ?ob) (handempty))
